Hi, I am building a deep tech software as a medical device that will hopefully save thousands of lives.

I am looking for a brilliant engineer who has the following characteristics:

People that are exceptional -Brilliant -given an idea and needs no further direction -can move mountains - Scrappy/industrious Deep skill set in machine learning / computer science Purpose driven and intrinsically motivated -Bonus points if interest in machine learning, healthcare, or building a better future Humility, Trust Interested in ideas and innovation, passionate, bright-eyed Team Player Skewed Introverted
